divs: Sighting DetailsMe and my wife and son were in the yard jumping on the trampoline at 8.00 pm Friday 3-17-08 when we looked in the sky and saw a star like object moving at high rate of speed just above cloud high . A lot faster then a jet are anything the usa has got.
